{"id": 1797, "genre": 1001, "title": "对你来说，什么样的婚姻状态称得上理想？", "description": "或者说，什么样的婚姻状态会让没结婚的你愿意结婚？", "record_count": 5875, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170711172353MAQuemZ7h0kCRsFO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-12T03:00:06Z", "options": [{"id": 220928, "content": "互相包容，爱好不同，三观一致。独立又依赖，为鸡毛蒜皮的小事争吵，一个吻就和好。窝里斗，对外一致。互相欣赏，携手成长。细水流长，平淡而不乏味。把对方当作最珍惜的，离开父母以后，相互陪伴走过漫长人生的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065613}, {"id": 224768, "content": "爱 信任 承担 包容", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830488}, {"id": 220673, "content": "回家之后就不能总抱着手机了", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 220929, "content": "一切顺心相互理解。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076099}, {"id": 221185, "content": "这可能要她才知道了吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076941}, {"id": 221697, "content": "信任", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077141}, {"id": 220930, "content": "笑点一致 接的住所有抛过来的梗", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076245}, {"id": 221186, "content": "婚姻是生产力不丰富情况下两个人通过合伙过日子来降低生活成本的权宜之计，所以共产主义实现后就不用结婚了，想想真是美滋滋", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422542}, {"id": 220931, "content": "为彼此考虑，珍惜对方", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 899167}, {"id": 220932, "content": "心灵相通", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822334}, {"id": 221188, "content": "\n我们共享雾霭流岚虹霓，仿佛永远分离，却又终身相依", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052498}, {"id": 221444, "content": "我爸我妈这样就挺好。一个人拿主意另一个人无条件认同。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871628}, {"id": 222212, "content": "一起进步，而不是一个人进步", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079902}, {"id": 220677, "content": "一起追剧，对方不会偷偷多看一集，更不会剧透", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 220933, "content": "像亲人一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076134}, {"id": 221189, "content": "爱对方的一切，包容所有，因为想和对方一起生活而结婚。陪伴对方的所有时期，无论她/他是否低谷… …遗憾的是我还未找到那位可以与我一般意志的另一半", "image": "img/option/option/201707122111135F7WJwQkS4RxOhrq.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 845806}, {"id": 220934, "content": "我想的 你恰好懂 我需要 你恰好在", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076587}, {"id": 221190, "content": "你烧饭、我洗碗；石头剪刀布，输的去拖地", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172715}, {"id": 220679, "content": "家务怎样分摊，要友好协商决定", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 220935, "content": "相互珍惜，为对方着想", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 899167}, {"id": 222727, "content": "包容，理解，关爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081964}, {"id": 220936, "content": "听进去对方的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 899167}, {"id": 221192, "content": "他是我老公的前提是他也是我最好的朋友 两个人都是最懂对方的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076961}, {"id": 237576, "content": "有原则却又求新求变，有主见却又听得进劝~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597012}, {"id": 220681, "content": "各花各的钱，大笔支出AA", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 221193, "content": "婚姻是种长期合作关系；成本和风险很高", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327659}, {"id": 220938, "content": "我对你好\n你对我好", "image": "img/option/option/20170712124630xIJAhu92gpCjVGFd", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076594}, {"id": 222986, "content": "听该听的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082368}, {"id": 224778, "content": "相敬如宾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088136}, {"id": 221195, "content": "自己觉得理想的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031533}, {"id": 225035, "content": "十年之后你们都变了，变得比十年前更加适合在一起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089602}, {"id": 220940, "content": "尊重彼此，给彼此空间和时间，互相陪伴的时候是舒服惬意的，遇到困难的时候是共同面对的", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075661}, {"id": 221196, "content": "婚姻就相互理解，相互宽容。多站在别人角度多想想。多换位思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076975}, {"id": 220941, "content": "保持相互了解的意愿与行动", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916002}, {"id": 221197, "content": "婚姻就是哭时候有人疼，累的时候有人靠。总是把最好的留给你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076975}, {"id": 220942, "content": "可以随时愉快的聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056670}, {"id": 221198, "content": "品位相近", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686925}, {"id": 220943, "content": "可以相互依赖 人格平等而自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951985}, {"id": 221199, "content": "不当你的世界，只做你的肩膀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880037}, {"id": 220944, "content": "珍惜对方，彼此肯为对方的快乐受委屈", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076601}, {"id": 221200, "content": "分事明理", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907646}, {"id": 223504, "content": "她也喜欢二次元，爱miku", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978457}, {"id": 220945, "content": "两个人在一起久了不会烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658287}, {"id": 220946, "content": "开心的时候互相喜欢，不开心的时候互相不嫌烦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 221202, "content": "白天各自追求自己的人生理想，携手相伴，相互鼓励。晚上和谐入眠，久睡不腻。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110414}, {"id": 220947, "content": "我是爱你的，你是自由的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508758}, {"id": 228115, "content": "很有趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099683}, {"id": 220948, "content": "一起在打拼事业 更努力工作让家更稳定", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035863}, {"id": 221204, "content": "互为依靠，精神解药，身体依赖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076986}, {"id": 222228, "content": "仍然像在谈恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080082}]}